---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — Thee Rainers">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="description" content="Thee Rainers is the operating system built from the floor up — from film, data, and the body itself. For athletes whose ambition has outpaced their gym." />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Identity: heading full-width, then balanced 2-col -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-20 border-b border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">

      <!-- Full-width heading — no competing with image -->
      <div class="mb-16 md:mb-20">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Thee Rainers · @theerainers</p>
        <h1 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.82]"
          style="font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);">
          Built from<br/>the floor up.
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- 2-col: text left, image right — heights naturally match -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] gap-16 md:gap-24 items-start">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-7">
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/55 leading-relaxed" style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.25vw, 1.125rem); max-width: 520px;">
            The Blueprints is the operating system I built because the gym gave me fragments. Athletes want to develop with structure — not more reps. I had to build it from the floor up, from what the data and my own body gave me.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/30 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[520px]">
            The mission is to produce people who think, move, and operate with systemic precision — because that is what this body was built for.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:block">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden border border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
            <img
              src="/images/coaching_amateurboxerinnetherlands.png"
              alt="Coaching — Netherlands."
              width="1200" height="1500"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            />
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mt-4">In the work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cinematic photo strip — visual break between sections -->
  <div class="w-full overflow-hidden bg-[#0A0A0A]" style="height: 50vw; max-height: 580px; min-height: 260px;">
    <img
      src="/images/winning_firstfight_withoutcoach.jpg"
      alt="Thee Rainers"
      width="1200" height="800"
      loading="lazy"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- The Method + Scripture + CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-20 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">

      <!-- What We Do -->
      <div class="border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 pt-20 mb-20">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-12">What We Do</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col divide-y divide-[#0A0A0A]/8">

          <a href="/vault"
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] py-8 gap-3 sm:gap-12 items-start group hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-200">
            <div class="pt-0.5">
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">The Protocol</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-[10px] tracking-wide mt-1">Blueprints · /vault →</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] text-base uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight mb-2">You train hard. The system makes it transfer.</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Step-by-step modules — stance, footwork, output — built in the order your body needs them. Not fragments. Not general advice. The operating system your gym never gave you.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/qa"
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] py-8 gap-3 sm:gap-12 items-start group hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-200">
            <div class="pt-0.5">
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">The Room</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-[10px] tracking-wide mt-1">Monthly Q&A · Live →</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] text-base uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight mb-2">The standard in that room will raise yours.</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">One hour. One Saturday per month. Camera on. You bring what is not transferring — we map it to the lever live. The fighters in that room are working. That environment is the product.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] py-8 gap-3 sm:gap-12 items-start">
            <div class="pt-0.5">
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">The Correction</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-[10px] tracking-wide mt-1">Every session · One fix</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] text-base uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight mb-2">One precision fix compounds. Five tips do not.</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every session ends with one thing: a correction you run in your next training session. Remove one wrong pattern. That is worth more than a hundred reps added. Twelve months of that is a different fighter.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/command"
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] py-8 gap-3 sm:gap-12 items-start group hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-200">
            <div class="pt-0.5">
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">The Summit</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-[10px] tracking-wide mt-1">Private Architecture →</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] text-base uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight mb-2">When the group is not enough.</p>
              <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">One system built entirely around your fight, your body, your mind. No templates. No cohorts. Application only. Not everyone qualifies. For the ones who do, there is no ceiling.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

        </div>

        <!-- Social follow bar -->
        <div class="mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Follow the work</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-3">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/theerainers" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 group hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">Instagram</span>
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px]">331K →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@theerainers" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 group hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">TikTok</span>
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px]">90K →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Rainers" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 group hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">YouTube</span>
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px]">15K →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/theerainers" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 group hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">Facebook</span>
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px]">110K →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.threads.net/@theerainers" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 group hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">Threads</span>
              <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-[10px]">20K →</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Scripture -->
      <div class="border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 pt-20 mb-20">
        <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A]/55 uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.88] max-w-[640px] mb-6"
          style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);">
          "Run in such a way as to get the prize. Every athlete exercises self-control in all things. So I do not run aimlessly; I do not box as one beating the air."
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">1 Corinthians 9:24–26 · The Source Code</p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 pt-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-8">
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/30 text-sm max-w-[400px] leading-relaxed">The system is built. The next step is yours.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 shrink-0">
          <a href="/vault" class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white whitespace-nowrap">Get the Blueprints →</a>
          <a href="/footwork-foundation" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-[#0A0A0A]/15 text-[#0A0A0A]/40 bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:border-[#0A0A0A]/30 hover:text-[#0A0A0A]/60 whitespace-nowrap">Start Free →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
